# Cline Rules

Before editing code, read:

1. AGENTS.md
2. docs/AI_CODING_AGENTS.md
3. .cursor/rules/karpathy-guidelines.mdc
4. docs/ENGINEERING_RULES.md
5. docs/NAMING_CONVENTIONS.md
6. The nearest folder README.md

For Next.js framework changes, read the relevant installed docs under node_modules/next/dist/docs/.

Keep changes small, do not touch unrelated files, and report validation results.
